    },
    {
      "id": "RWfqzMMcJVn41jf2yooWi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -111.8203125,
      "y": 1197.78125,
      "width": 906.6976318359375,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#846358",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 90,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ao",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1981585541,
      "version": 180,
      "versionNonce": 175838155,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782043108274,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Instead of having Null-Pointer, code will now instead have NullObject which will be emtpy dummy object\nand won't throw errors",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Instead of having Null-Pointer, code will now instead have NullObject which will be emtpy dummy object and won't throw errors",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6cWOTknnL0zpx09Oc41Wo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -104.36358642578125,
      "y": 1314.4453125,
      "width": 907.5865478515625,
      "height": 54,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ap",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 341198821,
      "version": 853,
      "versionNonce": 1055114437,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782043264053,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Consider this example of Strategy Pattern where we were creating Robots with Flying capability. \nBut suppose some robots can't fly. Will we keep their corresponding Composition attributed null?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Consider this example of Strategy Pattern where we were creating Robots with Flying capability. \nBut suppose some robots can't fly. Will we keep their corresponding Composition attributed null?",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "OrmUdnFE2VtyGtfLwprh6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -109.10968017578125,
      "y": 1393.2109375,
      "width": 907.5865478515625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1072895877,
      "version": 1145,
      "versionNonce": 1401395301,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782043750081,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Keeping Null-Pointer is never safe, it can easily throw errors and in turn will lead loads of\nconditional checks.\nSo instead in this case we keep instance of NoFly object as IFlyStrategy in Robot.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Keeping Null-Pointer is never safe, it can easily throw errors and in turn will lead loads of conditional checks.\nSo instead in this case we keep instance of NoFly object as IFlyStrategy in Robot.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1Xx2AnReYdPeO0NOoj7Cg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 271.1410172653403,
      "y": 1515.3796088458587,
      "width": 131.45792853454248,
      "height": 67.4057468161409,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ar",
      "roundness": null,
