      "updated": 1782044017622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In Command-pattern, we also discussed, that on remote the 1st command which we will given\non all buttons will be No-Command.\nHere also in the actual implementation of Command, we can have NoCommand class to avoid\nchecking and directly call object methods.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In Command-pattern, we also discussed, that on remote the 1st command which we will given on all buttons will be No-Command.\nHere also in the actual implementation of Command, we can have NoCommand class to avoid checking and directly call object methods.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
